quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Na ha se Rona ba atollotseng sefuba sa hau
  94,2,Ra u imulla moroalo
  94,3,O neng o u roba mokokotlo
  94,4,Le hona ho tumisa boemo ba hau
  94,5,Ruri! Ho teng topollo mathateng ohle
  94,6,Ruri! Mathateng oohle ho teng topollo
  94,7,"Kahoo, ha u lopolotsoe, tsitlellela ho sebetsa ka thata"
  94,8,U retellehele ho Mong`a hau